description: This Chainlink VRF common Chukcha purrs with a rating of 16, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 32, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, 5 for East, Box for South, and 5 for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/30162-15451-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Chukcha [32 Votes, Common]
